<br />
    Maybe I can answer a couple of your questions, and maybe i am just filling space~
<br />
    As far as twisting your DoT's with your drum in a group, Im pretty sure thats gonna really make the mob your on very unhappy with you. So much so that you will die, considering how hard mobs at those lvls can hit. Let the warriors take the hits, that why their there  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />Bards in a group generally arent there to deal a ton of damage, but to increase the overall efficiancy of the group. We add more to a group than any other class IMO, and its not by stackin dots.
<br />
   Moving on, Flowing Thought items do help us regen mana, but as far as conserving mama, I think those effects are restricted to spells in such a way that they will not work with bard songs that use mana. Could be wrong about that though.
